                        "4. Isocitrate dehydrogenase: Isocitrate → α-ketoglutarate + CO₂ + NADH",
                        "5. α-ketoglutarate dehydrogenase: α-ketoglutarate → Succinyl-CoA + CO₂ + NADH",
                        "6. Succinyl-CoA synthetase: Succinyl-CoA → Succinate + GTP",
