            "Oxidative phosphorylation via the ETC and ATP synthase generates the majority of ATP in aerobic metabolism",
            "Fermentation regenerates NAD⁺ without an ETC; yields only 2 ATP per glucose",
            "Microbes are extraordinarily metabolically diverse: chemolithotrophs, phototrophs, and anaerobic respirers occupy every geochemical niche",
