                            "Quinolone resistance: mutations in gyrA/parC target genes",
                            "Rifampicin resistance: rpoB mutations in RNA polymerase",
                            "VRE: D-Ala-D-Lac substitution prevents vancomycin binding",
                            "Macrolide resistance: erm methylases modify 23S rRNA"
