                            specificity: "Adhesin–receptor specificity determines tissue tropism and host range",
                            examples: ["H. pylori — BabA adhesin binds Lewis b blood group antigen on gastric epithelium", "Influenza HA binds α-2,6-sialic acid (human URT) or α-2,3-sialic acid (avian, deep human lung)"]
