                        examples: ["Streptococcus pneumoniae (>90 capsular serotypes — immunotype basis of vaccine)", "Neisseria meningitidis (A, B, C, W, Y, X serogroups)", "Klebsiella pneumoniae", "Haemophilus influenzae type b"],
                        someFactual: "S. aureus lacks a classical polysaccharide capsule but has protein A (binds IgG Fc region — blocks opsonisation)"
