                    "2. When O₂ is present (E°' O₂/H₂O = +0.82 V), organisms preferentially use O₂ — higher ΔE°' → more energy",
                    "3. Denitrification is enzymatically repressed by O₂ (nitrate reductase gene expression inhibited by O₂)",
                    "4. In anoxic zones (waterlogged soil, sediment, biofilm interior), NO₃⁻ becomes the most energetically favourable available acceptor → denitrification proceeds"
