                    "2. Crop rotation with legumes restores soil N without synthetic fertiliser",
                    "3. Avoid compaction and waterlogging → reduces denitrification losses",
                    "4. Nitrification inhibitors (e.g. DMPP) slow NH₄⁺ → NO₃⁻ conversion → reduces N leaching",
