                    "3. Without excretion, cell would swell and lyse",
                    "4. Contractile vacuole collects excess water and rhythmically expels it (osmoregulation)",
                    "5. Marine water is approximately iso-osmotic to intracellular fluid — no net water entry by osmosis",
                    "Result: No contractile vacuole needed in marine/parasitic protists living in iso-osmotic conditions"
