                "Cell number: Nt = N₀ × 2ⁿ = N₀ × e^(μt)",
                "Specific growth rate: μ = (ln N₂ − ln N₁) / (t₂ − t₁)",
                "Monod equation: μ = μmax × [S] / (Ks + [S])",
                "Dilution rate: D = F / V",
                "Chemostat steady state: μ = D",
                "CFU/mL: colonies ÷ (volume plated × dilution factor)"
