                    highCharge: "ATP abundant → inhibits PFK-1, pyruvate kinase, isocitrate dehydrogenase, citrate synthase; slows respiration",
                    lowCharge: "AMP/ADP accumulate → activate PFK-1, AMP-activated protein kinase (AMPK); accelerate respiration"
