                        coupled: "Glucose + ATP → Glucose-6-phosphate + ADP   ΔG°' = −16.7 kJ/mol (exergonic — spontaneous)",
                        lesson: "ATP hydrolysis is coupled to glucose phosphorylation by sharing Pi as a common intermediate"
