                    components: "Concentration term + electrical term (for ions); both must be overcome by ATP",
                    example: "Na⁺/K⁺-ATPase: ΔG for pumping one Na⁺ out ≈ +12 kJ/mol; 3 Na⁺ = +36 kJ/mol; ATP provides ~50 kJ/mol → thermodynamically feasible"
