                    keyEnzyme: "Fatty acid synthase (FAS) — multifunctional enzyme complex in animals",
                    startingMaterial: "Acetyl-CoA (must be exported from mitochondria via citrate shuttle)",
                    coFactors: "NADPH (from pentose phosphate pathway and malic enzyme)",
