                    "Step 1: Each glucose produces 2 pyruvate (glycolysis)",
                    "PDC: 2 pyruvate → 2 acetyl-CoA + 2 NADH (PDC produces 2 NADH, not Krebs cycle proper)",
                    "Krebs cycle runs twice (2 acetyl-CoA):",
                    "  - Steps 3, 4, 8 each produce 1 NADH per turn × 2 turns = 6 NADH",
                    "Total from Krebs cycle alone: 6 NADH",
                    "Total including PDC: 8 NADH from Krebs+PDC combined"
