            "Auxin drives phototropism and gravitropism through differential cell elongation",
            "Photoperiodism is controlled by the length of the dark period, detected via phytochrome",
            "Gibberellin promotes germination by inducing α-amylase synthesis in the aleurone layer",
            "Ethylene promotes fruit ripening, senescence, and abscission",
            "Vernalisation and photoperiodism ensure flowering is synchronised with the appropriate season",
            "Plant tissue culture exploits totipotency for micropropagation and transgenic plant production",
