                        uniqueFeatures: ["Multinucleate (syncytium)", "Myofibrils — organised arrays of actin and myosin", "T-tubules — invaginations of plasma membrane for rapid signal transmission", "Sarcoplasmic reticulum — specialised smooth ER for Ca²⁺ storage/release"]
