                        "Protection — skull protects brain; ribcage protects heart and lungs; vertebral column protects spinal cord",
                        "Movement — bones act as levers; muscles pull on bones to create motion",
                        "Mineral storage — stores 99% of body's calcium and 85% of phosphorus",
                        "Blood cell production — red bone marrow is the site of haematopoiesis",
                        "Energy storage — yellow bone marrow stores adipose (fat)"
