                    imaging: "CT/MRI adrenal glands; pituitary MRI; thyroid ultrasound; nuclear medicine (¹²³I thyroid scan, MIBG for phaeochromocytoma)",
                    geneticTesting: "MEN1/MEN2 mutations in multiple endocrine neoplasia syndromes"
