                    "7. Conformational change → tropomyosin moves → actin active sites exposed",
                    "8. Myosin heads bind actin → cross-bridge cycle → contraction",
                    "9. When stimulation stops: Ca²⁺ pumped back into SR by SERCA pumps (ATP-dependent)",
                    "10. Ca²⁺ levels fall → tropomyosin returns to blocking position → relaxation"
