                    "4. Peripheral chemoreceptors detect ↓PO₂ and ↑PCO₂",
                    "5. Signals to medullary respiratory centre → increased neural drive",
                    "6. Respiratory rate and tidal volume increase",
                    "7. More CO₂ expelled; PO₂ maintained"
