                    HLAMatching: "Better HLA match between donor and recipient → lower rejection risk",
                    immunosuppression: ["Calcineurin inhibitors (tacrolimus, cyclosporin) — inhibit T cell IL-2 production", "Mycophenolate — inhibits lymphocyte proliferation", "Corticosteroids — broad anti-inflammatory", "Belatacept — CTLA4-Ig; blocks CD28 costimulation"]
